data.description: Welcome home to this adorable Cape Cod home, sitting on an acre lot. With 4 bedrooms and 2 1/2 bathrooms, this two-story gem has a finished basement as well to offer ample space for everyone. The main floor features hardwood floors throughout a cozy living area that seamlessly flows into a formal dining room, just a few steps from the kitchen. There is a bedroom, full bathroom, and the laundry room also located on the main level. Step onto the deck, and you'll find yourself in a spacious, fenced-in backyard, offering room for endless possibilities. The property stretches well beyond the existing fence line.Venture upstairs to find three more bedrooms and a full bathroom. A cleverly designed laundry chute ensures laundry day is a breeze, making life just a little bit easier.In the finished basement, an oversized open rec room beckons for family fun and relaxation. There's additional space that would be great for an office or gaming area. And let's not forget the convenience of a half bathroom downstairs.This home is all about casual comfort and space to play. This home is ready for your personal touch. With a few updates, this home will be a place to kick back, relax, and make some awesome memories.
